metadata.name: Kabosu #1
metadata.description:
This collection was created to honor Kabosu, better known as “Doge".

When her puppy mill shut down in 2008, she was adopted by a Japanese kindergarten teacher and named after a citrus fruit.

Kabosu continues to influence culture even now, and has been referenced in popular video games as well as song lyrics. She's even inspired her own cryptocurrency — the first to be based on a meme.

Bold lines, vibrant colors, and a galaxy texture were used to convey to Kabosu’s impact, and to celebrate her legacy as one of the best memes of the last decade.
